    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one, and it seriously still has that new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been meticulously loved and kept in top-notch shape, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
