    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a superlative example of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is delivered by the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six, offering a broad torque curve and immediate throttle response. The 6-speed longitudinal gearbox provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for optimized damping characteristics. This specimen remains in concours-level condition, featuring flawless paint depth and a pristine undercarriage. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, it exhibits no mechanical play in the bushings or synchromesh, ensuring a telepathic connection between driver and tarmac.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
