    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolutely flawless example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents in true showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional-grade ceramic coating, free of any stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows zero signs of wear, while the original floor mats have been protected since day one. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, switch, and sensor functions exactly as it did the day it was delivered. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a turn-key, collector-quality vehicle that drives as smoothly as it looks. No accidents, non-smoker, and always hand-washed.",
      "price": 48500.0,
