    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this absolute gem! I\u2019m parting ways with my pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in spectacular shape\u2014inside and out. It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and looks just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, this is the one for you. Smooth, spotless, and totally ready for a new home. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
