    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-division engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing. The powertrain delivers a linear 333 hp to the rear wheels through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement, rod bearing replacement, and a full VANOS overhaul, ensuring structural integrity and mechanical longevity. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, providing the communicative steering and neutral handling balance the E46 is renowned for. Every bushing, seal, and fluid has been maintained to an exacting standard, presenting a turn-key opportunity for the discerning collector.",
